          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Coming to us from the auteur mind of Yoko Taro is his latest game ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Voice Of Cards: The Isle Dragon Roars",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ",",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "a unique turn-based RPG presented as a card-based Tabletop RPG, complete with a Game Master and dice rolls. A dragon has awoken and threatens the livelihoods of everyone in the land. Motivated by the rewards alone, it is up to Ash and his monster companion Mar to go against the odds and defeat the dragon. ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
