      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "While I wouldn’t call it a bad game, ultimately, ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Voice Of Cards: The Isle Dragon Roars",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " is a game betrayed by its own marketing. If this wasn’t sold as Yoko Taro’s next big project and a deconstruction of the RPG genre, I would’ve been way more forgiving to this but in the end, all I’m left with is disappointment and emptiness over what could have been.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
